videos.headline: Brooks draws in Tarleton's D to set up Dickinson's slam
videos.description: Eli Brooks attacks the paint and dishes to Hunter Dickinson for the two-handed Michigan jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Brooks draws in Tarleton's D to set up Dickinson's slam) 2021/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moussa Diabate gets T'd up for taunting after massive slam
videos.description: Moussa Diabate receives a technical foul for yelling in a defender's face after the two-handed flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Moussa Diabate gets T'd up for taunting after massive slam) 2021/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dickinson flushes two-handed jam with ease for Michigan
videos.description: Hunter Dickinson posts up his defender and gets to the basket with ease for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dickinson flushes two-handed jam with ease for Michigan) 2021/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan's Brooks dishes no-look dime to Houstan for the 3
videos.description: Eli Brooks shows off his vision with a no-look pass to Caleb Houstan in the corner for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Michigan's Brooks dishes no-look dime to Houstan for the 3) 2021/11/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dickinson and Diabate rock the rim to help Michigan pull away
